                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "1USAMHG"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " fixed frequency cyclotron"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Thin Zr, Mo and Ti foils with natural isotopic",
                " composition, and ZnS vacuum evaporated onto mylar",
                " foils in the case of sulfur.",
                "The targets were prepared to Be 2-5 mg/cm2 in thickness",
                " (about 300 keV energy attenuation).",
                "The evenness of the samples was measured by using beta",
                " thickness gauge.",
                "Zr: 99.89% purity, 3.51 mg/cm2 thick, <2% evenness",
                "Mo: 99.9% purity, 4.992 mg/cm2 thick, <3% evenness",
                "Ti: 99.4% purity, 4.525 mg/cm2 thick, <3% evenness",
                "ZnS: reagent grade, 1.65 mg/cm2, <1% evenness"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "D4PI",
                "PROPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "STTA",
                "GSPEC",
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The initial bombarding deuteron energy was",
                " 7.78+/-0.005 MeV.",
                "The beam current was measured by means of a Faraday-",
                " cup equipped with secondary electron suppressor, and",
                " was calibrated to counts/Coulomb precisely.",
                "To catch the recoiled reaction products mylar foils",
                " were used.",
                "Chemical separation was applied to get the reaction",
                " product in carrier free form. To measure the yield of",
                " the chemical separation long lived radioisotopes were",
                " used as tracers.",
                "4pi-beta counter was used to measure the activity of",
                " the samples.",
                "Coincidence measurement technique also was used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DECAY"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
